== Description of Disbelief in Tāghūt:

1. To believe that worshipping anything other than Allāh is false, to abandon
   it, and to hate it.

2. To consider its followers disbelievers and to oppose them.

== The Main Heads of Tāghūt:

Tāghūts are many, but the main five are:

1. Iblīs (Satan) -- may Allāh curse him.
2. Anyone worshipped besides Allāh and is pleased with that worship.
3. Anyone who calls people to worship himself.
4. Anyone who claims knowledge of the unseen (ghayb).
5. Anyone who rules by laws other than what Allāh has revealed.